'''Jeff Coopwood''' (born [[June 29]], [[1950s#1958|1958]]) is an American actor who provided the voice for [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Quarsh Panaka/Legends|Quarsh Panaka]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace (video game)|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'' video game]], ''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]'', and ''[[Star Wars: Episode I: Battle for Naboo]]''.

